ic''\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.superyachttimes.com/yacht-news/superyacht-big-mak-for-sale-through-burgess-and-edmiston|title=Superyacht Big Mak for sale through Burgess and Edmiston|publisher=SuperYacht Times|accessdate=2018-06-15}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1999\n| 47\n| ''You & Me''\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.superyachttimes.com/yacht-news/superyacht-sea-dweller-sold|title=Superyacht Sea Dweller sold|publisher=SuperYacht Times|accessdate=2018-06-15}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1999\n| 39.10\n| ''Red Sapphire I''\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.superyachttimes.com/yacht-news/red-sapphire-outside-monaco|title=The speedy superyacht Red Sapphire I outside Monaco|publisher=SuperYacht Times|accessdate=2018-06-15}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==2000\u20132009==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Length overall in meters\n! Name\n! Picture\n! Reference\n\n|-\n| 2000\n| 34.84\n| ''Alcor''\n| \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.superyachttimes.com/superyachts/alcor/news|title=Superyacht Alcor|publisher=SuperYacht Times|accessdate=2018-06-15}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2000\n| 30.66\n| ''Ammoun of London''\n| \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.superyachttimes.com/superyachts/ammoun-of-london/specifications|title=Superyacht Ammoun of London|publisher=SuperYacht Times|accessdate=2018-06-15}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2000\n| 30.70\n| ''Pokrov II''\n| \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.superyachttimes.com/yacht-news/new-owner-for-31m-superyacht-pokrov-ii|title=New owner for 31m superyacht Pokrov II|publisher=SuperYacht Times|accessdate=2018-06-15}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2001\n| 39.80\n| ''Happy T''\n| \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.superyachttimes.com/yacht-news/recent-superyacht-sales-by-cni|title=Recent superyacht sales by CNI|publisher=SuperYacht Times|accessdate=2018-06-15}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2001\n| 39.40\n| ''Lady Azul''\n| \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.superyachttimes.com/yacht-news/brokerage-deal-of-the-week-the-39m-superyacht-lady-azul|title=Brokerage Deal of the Week: the 39m superyacht Lady Azul|publis